<script>
  window._profile = window._profile || {};
  window._profile.geo = window._profile.geo || {};
  window._profile.geo.zip = "90011";
  window._profile.geo.city = "los angeles";
  window._profile.geo.state = "california";
  window._profile.geo.dma = "los angeles";
  window._profile.geo.region = window._profile.geo.region || {
    'rom': "",
    'rop': ""
  }
  // user.<whatever> are my profile scripts
  // profile.<whatever> are the profile parameters
  window._profile.rndm = "29";

  window._profile.flags = window._profile.flags || {}
  window._profile.flags.reEnable = ""

  window.onload = function () {
    document.addEventListener('pEmbed', function (e) {
      if (window._geo) {
        //console.log("pEmbed: pEmbed Called");
      }
    })
    var e = new CustomEvent('pEmbed', {
      'e': 'geo_ready'
    });
    document.dispatchEvent(e);
    var e2 = new CustomEvent('profile-ready', {
      'e': 'profile-ready'
    });
    document.dispatchEvent(e2);
  }
</script>
